<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I have camped the green bubble through about 125 to 150 times across assorted different trips to the fabulous Cazic Thule...In that time I would estimate the AoF to spawn an average of one in eight to one in ten.   I have seen him spawn three times in a row and not once in over twenty spawns so he has lots of variety.  Once a group of guildmates saw him spawn eight out of twelve spawns.  To the best of my knowlege I have killed the AoF fifteen times and he dropped the ravenscale chestguard once.  There was no rogue in our party,  but my guildmate won the lotto and later sold it at a very reasonable price to a delighted rogue we both knew.  Best of luck all,  this is one of the best fights in the game in my experience so keep on camping.</font></td></tr></table>
